---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="container footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <span class="footer-logo">☯ 老子道</span>
      <p class="footer-tagline">道法自然 · 量化有道</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-links">
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>项目</h4>
        <a href="/projects">开源项目</a>
        <a href="/research">研究文章</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>链接</h4>
        <a href="https://github.com/laozdao" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
        <a href="/about">关于我</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>© {currentYear} laozdao · 以道御术，以术证道</p>
      <p class="footer-quote">"上善若水，水善利万物而不争" —— 《道德经》第八章</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .site-footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
    padding: 3rem 0 2rem;
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .footer-inner {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .footer-brand {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .footer-tagline {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .footer-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .footer-col h4 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .footer-col a {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .footer-col a:hover {
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .footer-bottom p {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .footer-quote {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .footer-links {
      gap: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
